Raspberry Pi Router/Server simple control script.
   * by ph0x0en1x (https://ph0en1x.net). 

Hardware:
 + Raspberry Pi 3 Model B
 + 128x64 OLED display
 + 5 switches
 + Real time clock board
 + Thermo sensor
 + RGB LED

Script features:
 + Showing simple menu on display in 5 lines,
 + Showing current BTC, ETH, USD, EUR rates,
 + Showing CPU and BOX temp, MEMORY load and internet connection status,
 + Idle mode animations on display,
 + Warnings by LED and BUZZER when internet connection is lost,
 + Power OFF Raspberry Pi safely from menu.


Construction and Hardware part:
https://ph0en1x.net/104-raspberry-pi-handmade-server-router-hardware.html

Software part:
https://ph0en1x.net/105-raspberry-pi-handmade-server-router-software.html

